{%- comment -%}
  A LandingPage is just a stack of section blocks. Render the Sections bag at the
  Detail display type; each contained block renders through its Block-<Type> template,
  which supplies its own full-width band. No page chrome here (that is the layout).
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- for block in Model.ContentItem.Content.Sections.ContentItems -%}
  {{ block | shape_build_display: "Detail" | shape_render }}
{%- endfor -%}
